## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Redirects**: Do you want me to add Next.js redirects from old `/category/[slug]` URLs to new `/[slug]` URLs in `next.config.ts`? This is important if the old URLs are already indexed by Google.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 2. **Ad placeholders**: The visible "Advertisement" boxes take significant space. Should I remove them entirely since you're using Journey/Mediavine injection, or keep them as layout reservoirs?

> [!WARNING]
> 3. **Category slug inconsistencies**: Many tool pages pass wrong slugs (e.g., `slug: "math"` instead of `"math-calculators"`, `slug: "finance"` instead of `"finance-tools"`). Want me to fix all of these to match the canonical slugs in `config/site.ts`?

