1. `npm run build` — Verify no broken routes after folder rename
2. Check all category pages load at new URLs (e.g., `/math-calculators`)
3. Verify sitemap.xml output contains correct URLs
4. Check breadcrumbs on tool pages point to correct category URLs

### Manual Verification
- Browser test: Navigate through homepage → category → tool → breadcrumb back
- Verify mobile layout compactness improvements
- Check SEO meta tags via View Source on key pages
